var app=new Vue({el:"#app",data:{todos:[{text:"Learn JavaScript",done:!1},{text:"Learn Vue",done:!1},{text:"Build something awesome",done:!1}]},template:"<div class='container'>\n    <input id='input' type='text'>\n    <button @click=\"addItem\">Add</button>\n    <ol>\n      <li @click=\"todo.done = !todo.done\" v-bind:class=\"[todo.done ? 'complete' : 'active' ]\" v-for='todo in todos' >\n        <input type=\"checkbox\">\n        {{todo.text}}\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>",methods:{addItem(){let t=document.querySelector("#input");t.value.length>0&&app.todos.push({text:t.value})}}});